        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Get the Lead Out Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires community water systems serving populations of 3,300 or more to submit to the Environmental Protection Agency a plan to inventory and replace all the lead service lines of the system within 10 years.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
